trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the path points of a polyline annotation at run time.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir banepunkter en polygonlinje merknad på kjøretidspunktet.

trans-unit.source: A polyline must use coordinates relative to an annotation object, where (0,0) denotes the top-left coordinates and (100,100) denotes the bottom-right coordinates of the annotation.
trans-unit.target: En polygonlinje må bruke koordinatene i forhold til et objekt for merknaden, der (0,0) angir øverste venstre hjørne koordinater og (100,100) angir nedre høyre koordinatene for merknaden.

trans-unit.source: This property is not accessible at design time, when you should use the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolylineAnnotation.GraphicsPathPoints%2A> property instead.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er ikke tilgjengelig på utformingstidspunktet når du skal bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolylineAnnotation.GraphicsPathPoints%2A>egenskapen i stedet.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolylineAnnotation.GraphicsPathPoints%2A>

trans-unit.source: A GraphicsPath object with the polyline shape.
trans-unit.target: Et GraphicsPath-objekt med polygonlinje-formen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the path points of the polyline annotation at design time.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir banepunkter polygonlinje merknad ved utformingen.

trans-unit.source: A polyline must use coordinates relative to an annotation object, where (0,0) denotes the top-left coordinates and (100,100) denotes the bottom-right coordinates of the annotation.
trans-unit.target: En polygonlinje må bruke koordinatene i forhold til et objekt for merknaden, der (0,0) angir øverste venstre hjørne koordinater og (100,100) angir nedre høyre koordinatene for merknaden.

trans-unit.source: This property is not accessible at run time, when you should use the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolylineAnnotation.GraphicsPath%2A> property instead.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er ikke tilgjengelig på kjøretidspunktet, når du skal bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolylineAnnotation.GraphicsPath%2A>egenskapen i stedet.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolylineAnnotation.GraphicsPath%2A>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationPathPointCollection"></xref> object with the polyline shape.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AnnotationPathPointCollection"> </xref> objekt med polygonlinje-formen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a flag that determines whether an annotation should be placed using the free-draw mode.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir et flagg som bestemmer om en merknad plasseres ved hjelp av free-draw-modus.

trans-unit.source: Two different placement modes are supported when the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Annotation.BeginPlacement%2A> method is called.
trans-unit.target: To ulike plassering støttes når den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Annotation.BeginPlacement%2A>-metoden.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Annotation.BeginPlacement%2A>

trans-unit.source: Set the IsFreeDrawPlacement property to `true` to switch from the default mode to free-draw mode, which allows the user to freely-draw while moving the mouse cursor.
trans-unit.target: Angi egenskapen IsFreeDrawPlacement `true` å bytte fra standardmodus til free-draw-modus, som lar brukeren fritt-draw mens du flytter pekeren.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref> if an annotation should be placed using free-draw mode, otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>Hvis en merknad plasseres ved hjelp av free-draw-modus, ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default value is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
